title: Cant post on forums?
body:
Its says i need level 7 but I'm level 31.  Rito pls.
edit: It's happening on the Concepts and Creations tab.

replies.body:
Huzzah for quick and easy fixes xD! 

If this ever happens again, try using the [**Syncing Tool**](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool) really quick ^_^!
Looks like you just needed to give the boards a swift kick in the rear (by posting here). You should be all set now :P
